%I A396483 #9 Jun 02 2026 06:51:08
%S A396483 1,3,2,19,138,11591,657781
%N A396483 Number of undirected Hamiltonian cycles in the mod n square grid graph, reduced for symmetry (with rotations, reflections, and translations not counted as distinct).
%C A396483 Here a "mod n square grid graph" is a n X n graph with wrapping allowed, e.g., a path can make a 1 unit step between the left and the right edge (same row) or the top and the bottom edge (same column) of the graph.
